    "The proposed bio-semantic summarizing system consists of four steps:• Semantics of the text is used as a feature to obtain text summaries.",
    "We use biosemantic models to obtain semantics.",
    "These models are used to obtain our novel bigvectors.",
    "Big-vectors are semantic bag-of-words extensions of the sentences.",
    "Each sentence of the input text document is fed to the bio-semantic model to obtain semantic transformation of the sentence."
